tafsir[52]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,"Nuun : Haala fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol Al-Baqarah. Allah woondirii …óoo karambol, O woondiri kadi ko yim…ìe …ìen winndirta kon karammbi ma…ì…ìe …óin."
  68,2,"Aan Nulaa…óo a wonaa kaangaa…óo, sabu ko Allah neeminir-maa kon Annabaaku. Aan ko a danndii…óo e feetere nde …ìee sirkoo…ìe siforte."
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodan-maa mbarjaari ndi ta∆¥ondirtaa e ko dokkal hay gooto e dow Ma sabu kon ronnditagol nulal ngal e yim…ìe …ìen."
  68,4,"E ko pellet, hi…óa e jikku mawngu ngu Alqur'aana ardi e mun. Ko a jikkinir…óo ko woni e mayre kon e mbaadi timmundi."
  68,5,"Aray nde tinaa an, …ìee fennoo…ìe kadi yi'a."
  68,6,"√ëalnde goonga fee√±ata, anndoton ko hommbo e mo'on woni haangaa…óo."
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo …ìuri anndude oo√±ii…óo on e laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi …ìuri anndude feewu…ìe …ìen. Himo anndi ko kam…ìe woni majju…ìe …ìen, an woni feewu…óo e laawol Makko ngol."
  68,8,"An Nulaa…óo, wata a tewto fennoo…ìe ko addu…óaa kon."
  68,9,"Hi…ìe yi…ói si a newantono …ìe e innde diina, kam…ìe kadi …ìe newano-maa."
  68,10,"Wata a tewto kadi kala …óuu…óu…óo woondirgol meere, hoy…óo."
  68,11,"∆äuu…óu…óo √±o'ugol yim…ìe, …óuu…óu…óo yaarugol waddude yim…ìe fii senndira hakkunde ma…ì…ìe."
  68,12,"∆äuu…óu…óo ha…óugol mo∆¥∆¥ere, jaggitoowo jawle e teddule e pittaali yim…ìe, …óuu…óu…óo bakkaatu e geddi."
  68,13,"Yoora-…ìerndeejo, ≈ãi√±iraa…óo he…ìireede nii."
  68,14,"Fii tun o wonii jom jawdi e …ìi…ó…ìe, o townitanii gom…óingol Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on."
  68,15,"Si Aayeeje Amen …óen janngaama e makko, o wi'a: Ko tinndi adinoo…ìe nii."
  68,16,"Men wa…óanay mo maande nde momtotaako ka hoore kinal makko."
  68,17,"Men jarribor …ìee sirkoo…ìe kokke e heege, wano Men jarribornoo jey…ìe ngesa ba, fewndo …ìen woondunoo wonnde pellet, …ìe so√±iroyay mba subaka on, hi…ìe hittina fii wata miskiino √±aamu e mabba."
  68,18,"∆Åe ronki ittintinnde e woondoore ma…ì…ìe nden, wi'ugol : ""Si Allah ja…ìii""."
  68,19,"Allah wuurti yiite e mabba, nge √±aami ba tawi …ìe e mabba hari hi…ìe …óaani, …ìe waawaali du√±ugol yiite e mabba."
  68,20,"Mba …ìawliri wa jemma ni…ì…ìo."
  68,21,"∆Åe noddindiri bimmbi law."
  68,22,"∆Åe wi'i : Dawee ka ngesa mon ado waasu…ìe …ìen arude, si tawii ko on so√±oo…ìe mba."
  68,23,"∆Åe yahiri ka ngesa ma…ì…ìe hi…ìe sowndondira hakkunde ma…ì…ìe."
  68,24,"Hi…ìe wi'indira hakkunde ma…ì…ìe : miskiino woo naatataa ka ngesa ton hannde."
  68,25,"∆Åe dawidi e e…ì…ìoore …óawugol dim…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen."
  68,26,"Nde …ìe yi'noo ngesa mban no hu…ì…ìa, …ìe wi'i: Pellet, men majjii laawol amen ngol."
  68,27,"Wurin ko men ha…óaa…ìe su√±ugol dim…óe amen …óen, sabu ko men e…ì…ìunoo kon …óawugol miskim…ìe …ìen."
  68,28,"∆Åur…óo mo∆¥∆¥ude on wi'i: Mi wi'anaano on fewndo e…ì…ìuno…óon …óawugol waasu…ìe …ìen : haanii ka subhinano…óon Allah, tuubanon Mo?"
  68,29,"∆Åe wi'i : Senayee woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari men too√±itorii pittaali amen e…ì…ìugol …óawude waasu…ìe …ìen …óee dim…óe amen."
  68,30,"∆Åe ruttitii e konngol ma…ì…ìe ngol, hi…ìe felitoo."
  68,31,"∆Åe ninnsi …ìe wi'i : Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko men yawtunoo…ìe keeri, sabu ko men …óawi kon waasu…ìe …ìen haqqee ma…ì…ìe."
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana men ngesa mban. Ko ka Joomi amen tun woni ko menen men rer…óanta. Men jortorii Mo yaafuyee, me…óen …óa…ì…ìira Mo mo∆¥∆¥ere."
  68,33,"Ko sugu …óee lette ha…óeede arsike …óoo, woni ko Men lettirta yedday…ìe Men …ìen; ko lette laakara …óen non …ìuri mawnude, sinno hi…ìe anndunoo tii…óugol e duumagol …óe ngol."
  68,34,"Hulu…ìe Allah …ìen …óoftii yamirooje Makko …óen …ìe wo…ó…ótitii ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, ko pellet, hino woodani …ìe ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe, Aljannaaji neema, …ói …ìe neeminotoo e mun, ko aldaa e ta∆¥ondiral."
  68,35,"Kere Men wa…óay juul…ìe …ìen wano heefer…ìe …ìen ka njo…ìdi, wano sirkoo…ìe Makka …ìen aa∆¥ori …óum?"
  68,36,"Ko he…ìi on onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, si tawii hi…óon √±aawira ndee √±aawoore oo√±iinde?"
  68,37,"Kaa hi…óon mari Deftere, nde janngoton e mun wiide …óoftii…óo e goop…óo no fota?"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e nde Deftere, ko ko su…ìoyto…óon ka laakara."
  68,39,"Kaa ko aadiiji teentinaa…ói woodani on e Amen, wonnde pellet, ko ko √±aawan…óon ko'e-mon kon woodani on?"
  68,40,"An Nulaa…óo, lamndii …ìe wowlu …ìe ngol konngol …ìen, ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe fawtanii …ìe …óum?"
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidaa…ói woodani …ìe gaanin Allah, fotnay…ói …ìe e gom…óim…ìe …ìen njo…ìdi? Awa yo …ìe addu …óin kafidaa…ói ma…ì…ìe, si tawii ko e goonga …ìe woni nodditorde fotnugol …ìe e gom…óim…ìe …ìen ka njo…ìdi."
  68,42,"√ëalnde Darngal, kulol ngol fee√±ay, Joomi men fe√±√±ina korlal Makko ngal, yim…ìe …ìen noddee e sujjugol : gom…óim…ìe …ìen sujja, heddoo heefer…ìe …ìen e naafiqii…ìe …ìen tawde …ìe waawoytaa sujjude."
  68,43,"Hara gite ma…ì…ìe no heli, nimse e koyeera kadi no suddi …ìe. Ko tawde …ìe …óa…ì…ìirteno sujjangol Allah ka aduna, fewndo ka …ìe waawunoo …ìuri hanndeere nden."
  68,44,"An Nulaa…óo, accidam e kala fennu…óo ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Maa…óa; aray nde Men soggira …ìe e lette …óen sagara-sagara ka …ìe anndataa wonnde ko fewjoori e hoore ma…ì…ìe non."
  68,45,"Mi nennan …ìe tun e bakkatuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin see…óa. Ko pellet, pewje Am …óen e hoore heefer…ìe e fennoo…ìe …ìen ko tii…óu…óe. ∆Åe fuutotaako Lam, …ìe da…óoytaa kadi lette Am …óen."
  68,46,"Kaa hara an Nulaa…óo on a …óa…ì…ìir …ìe njo…ìdi e ko noddataa …ìe e mun kon, hara ko yo…ìugol …óum woni ko sattani …ìe haa tawata …ìe …óuurnoto ma? Tigi on, wanaa …óum. A …óa…ì…ìiraani …ìee njo…ìdi fes. Ko ha…ói …ìe non jokkugol ma?"
  68,47,"Kaa …ìe anndu fii wirnii…ói …óin, hara ko …óin woni ko …ìe winndirta ko waalantoo…ìe e hujjaaji …ói …ìe wennjire?"
  68,48,"An Nulaa…óo, mu√±√±or ko Joomi maa √±aawiri kon suynirgol …ìe nennaneede, hara a wa'aali wa Annabi Yuunusa wonndii…óo linngii ngii, ta∆¥inoo…óo e yim…ìe mun tuma o noddunoo Joomi makko ka niwre maayo e niwre linngii."
  68,49,"Si wanaa fii yurmeende Joomi makko nden hewtitike mo, ko pellet, linngii ngii bugotono mbo e wulaa hara ko o felnii…óo."
  68,50,"Joomi makko su…ìii mo, O wa…ói mo jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen."
  68,51,"Hay yeddu…ìe Allah …ìen yeddi Nulaa…óo Makko on, …ìe e…ì…ìiino yuwirgol ma gite ma…ì…ìe …óen, hakkee ko …ìe puttinatno maa gite, tuma …ìe nanata ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e maa…óa, hara hi…ìe wi'ira mbelee…óe e …óuurnagl goonga : Oo Nulaa…óo ardu…óo e ndee Deftere, ko haangaa…óo."
  68,52,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e maa…óa wonaali, si wanaa waaju e janntoore yim…ìe e jinna."
